column25:
It has been quite disappointing to see IF selling the tokens that myself and other investors have been holding since 2017. 
I still believe in the project, but there needs to be some transparency, especially around this type of decisions. It is not normal that we know of all this because some people were tracking the addresses.

The project is amazing, but there are some things that need to improve. 

The wiki is a great improvement compared to past documentation.

Keep up the good work! I'm sure we'll make it
